      "width": 205, "height": 195, "seed": 122, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Player joins mid-game\n       |\n2. Same spawn flow\n       |\n3. GameManager.OnNetworkSpawn\n   CLIENT path fires:\n       |\n4. OnStateValueChanged(\n     WaitingForPlayers,\n     CurrentState.Value)\n   MANUALLY called  FIX\n       |\n5. All subscribers fire:\n   CameraManager  OK\n   LightingManager  OK\n   DayPhaseHUD  OK\n       |\n6. Client sees correct phase", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Player joins mid-game\n       |\n2. Same spawn flow\n       |\n3. GameManager.OnNetworkSpawn\n   CLIENT path fires:\n       |\n4. OnStateValueChanged(\n     WaitingForPlayers,\n     CurrentState.Value)\n   MANUALLY called  FIX\n       |\n5. All subscribers fire:\n   CameraManager  OK\n   LightingManager  OK\n   DayPhaseHUD  OK\n       |\n6. Client sees correct phase", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

