      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Same client-side flow\n       |\n2. Server receives RPC\n       |\n3. FIRST: check GameState\n   == DayPhase\n       |\n4. If NOT DayPhase:\n   -> return; (reject RPC)\n       |\n5. If DayPhase:\n   -> proceed normally\n       |\n6. Cooking does NOT start\n   during Transition  FIX", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Same client-side flow\n       |\n2. Server receives RPC\n       |\n3. FIRST: check GameState\n   == DayPhase\n       |\n4. If NOT DayPhase:\n   -> return; (reject RPC)\n       |\n5. If DayPhase:\n   -> proceed normally\n       |\n6. Cooking does NOT start\n   during Transition  FIX", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

