      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Round ends\n       |\n2. DayPhaseCleanup fires\n       |\n3. CookingStation clears  OK\n   ServingCounter clears  OK\n       |\n4. PlayerInteraction\n   IS subscribed  FIX\n       |\n5. ClearCarriedItem()\n   CarriedItem = Empty  OK\n       |\n6. Player starts clean  OK", "textAlign": "left",
