      "width": 205, "height": 125, "seed": 422, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Player carrying dish\n       |\n2. Player disconnects\n       |\n3. OnClientDisconnected\n   fires in SpawnManager\n       |\n4. CHECK CarriedItem on\n   PlayerInteraction  NEW\n       |\n5. Log warning if carrying\n   -> then Despawn  FIX\n   (clean + auditable)", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Player carrying dish\n       |\n2. Player disconnects\n       |\n3. OnClientDisconnected\n   fires in SpawnManager\n       |\n4. CHECK CarriedItem on\n   PlayerInteraction  NEW\n       |\n5. Log warning if carrying\n   -> then Despawn  FIX\n   (clean + auditable)", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
