      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Host leaves game\n       |\n2. NetworkManager shuts\n   down on all clients\n       |\n3. OnNetworkDespawn fires\n   on GameManager\n       |\n4. Detect: !IsServer path\n   -> GameEvents.ResetAll()\n   -> SceneController\n      .ReturnToMenu()  FIX\n       |\n5. Clients return to menu\n   clean state  OK", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Host leaves game\n       |\n2. NetworkManager shuts\n   down on all clients\n       |\n3. OnNetworkDespawn fires\n   on GameManager\n       |\n4. Detect: !IsServer path\n   -> GameEvents.ResetAll()\n   -> SceneController\n      .ReturnToMenu()  FIX\n       |\n5. Clients return to menu\n   clean state  OK", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle", "version": 1, "versionNonce": 530, "isDeleted": false, "id": "m5_code_box",
