      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "text": "GameManager.cs          -> M1 (OnNetworkSpawn client catch-up)  |  M5 (OnNetworkDespawn host recovery)  |  M6 (remove StartTransition cleanup)\nPlayerInteraction.cs    -> M2 (phase guard on 5 RPCs)  |  M3 (subscribe to DayPhaseCleanup, add ClearCarriedItem)\nPlayerSpawnManager.cs   -> M4 (check + log CarriedItem before despawn in OnClientDisconnected)\nGameEvents.cs           -> No changes needed (ResetAll already exists for M5 use)", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "GameManager.cs          -> M1 (OnNetworkSpawn client catch-up)  |  M5 (OnNetworkDespawn host recovery)  |  M6 (remove StartTransition cleanup)\nPlayerInteraction.cs    -> M2 (phase guard on 5 RPCs)  |  M3 (subscribe to DayPhaseCleanup, add ClearCarriedItem)\nPlayerSpawnManager.cs   -> M4 (check + log CarriedItem before despawn in OnClientDisconnected)\nGameEvents.cs           -> No changes needed (ResetAll already exists for M5 use)", "lineHeight": 1.25
